title: Made In Sweden - Snakes In A Whole (1969) MP3@320
description:
Legenderay swedish instrumentalists. This is their second studio album from 1969.

Swedish psych/prog/jazz outfit rooted in the mid 1960's underground. Unusually for a band with such a name they were fronted by Polish ex-pat George Wadenius whose unique guitar style was key to their sound. The original trio format made 3 studio albums and a live album (plus contributions to a soundtrack work) before splitting up. All 3 members then joined Solar Plexus (9) (not at the same time). The reformation in the mid-1970's was more of a super-group also involving musicians from Finland.
